Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.46,0:00:04.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Wednesday Downtown,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.97,0:00:09.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So today we have prepared various theories for you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.51,0:00:11.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Matsumoto... Matsu... who're you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.76,0:00:17.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Finally, Yoshimoto has decided on a successor
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.00,0:00:18.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wow this is exciting
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.33,0:00:20.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What a historic day!  \N-Thanks for your kind words
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.64,0:00:21.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Surely there's no way
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.89,0:00:22.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That is, to tell the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.87,0:00:25.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sitting opposite Hamada-san is genuinely awful
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.62,0:00:27.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's really scary \N-Why do you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.58,0:00:30.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's like a car is constantly tailing me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.31,0:00:32.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The pressure is really not to be underestimated
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.82,0:00:35.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Matsumoto is really quite remarkable
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.51,0:00:37.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, it's time to get started!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.08,0:00:39.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Let’s get on with our first presenter please
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.76,0:00:48.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's Morita!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.11,0:00:49.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.39,0:00:51.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thank you for having me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.39,0:00:52.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Chief, chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.50,0:00:54.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thank you \N-Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.31,0:00:58.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You know, I recently heard something
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.34,0:01:01.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A ghost's lifespan is 200 years
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.32,0:01:02.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Does everyone know this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.52,0:01:04.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.04,0:01:05.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What is this lifespan you speak of?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.11,0:01:07.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A ghost is not completely dead, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.55,0:01:09.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Otherwise it wouldn't be appearing on this side
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.72,0:01:11.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Appearing as a ghost in the world of the living
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.80,0:01:14.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The life span of this state is 200 years
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.26,0:01:15.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Heh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.27,0:01:17.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, seeing ghosts of primitive people
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.65,0:01:19.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah! \N-Indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.16,0:01:20.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You never hear of such a thing, right?  \N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.80,0:01:23.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's weird that they have never appeared\N  -That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.08,0:01:24.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.34,0:01:25.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.48,0:01:28.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, what I bring to you today is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.19,0:01:31.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A related verification
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.24,0:01:32.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.77,0:01:35.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The theory I've brought is this:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.07,0:01:39.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It is actually difficult to get a person to say "heh?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.89,0:01:42.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.05,0:01:44.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After listening to what you just heard
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.35,0:01:46.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"Heh?" wasn't all that common a reaction
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.45,0:01:48.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Some said stuff like "Seriously?" \N-Indeed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.88,0:01:49.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So it's like this
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.91,0:01:50.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"Ha?" or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.79,0:01:52.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yoshimura was the only one that actually said it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.46,0:01:55.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He said "heh?" perfectly
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.13,0:01:57.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,200 years, that's all
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.50,0:01:58.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Heh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.53,0:02:01.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, is it true what you said about the ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.87,0:02:03.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Regarding that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.75,0:02:04.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's a lie
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.36,0:02:05.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Heh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.85,0:02:07.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.44,0:02:08.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, no, wait a minute
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:10.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You're saying "unbelievable", but first of all...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.58,0:02:14.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Do you actually believe in ghosts?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.45,0:02:17.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,As far as i'm concerned,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.08,0:02:20.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I like to share this type of rumor
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.29,0:02:21.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,When people hear stuff like this
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.72,0:02:23.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I always get this "heh?" reaction
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.35,0:02:27.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But, as it turns out, actual rumors can't be broadcast on TV
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.88,0:02:30.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So all the information we used this time is just patently false
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.49,0:02:31.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I see  \N-Fictitious
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.70,0:02:34.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, how many "heh"s can we get from them?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.64,0:02:36.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Let's find out
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.99,0:02:58.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It is actually difficult to get a person to say "heh?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.11,0:03:02.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And so, the instigator is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.88,0:03:01.95,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm in charge
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.95,0:03:02.93,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.46,0:03:06.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Morita
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.10,0:03:07.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Who is being targeted?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.37,0:03:11.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A junior of mine called Hyouroku
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.31,0:03:11.17,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hyouroku?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.17,0:03:12.21,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sounds like a folk tale
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.62,0:03:13.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A person with great respect for Morita
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.98,0:03:17.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He has appeared many times as a solo artist on Goodbye Live
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.02,0:03:16.60,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Looks like the type to say it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.62,0:03:18.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hyouroku
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.75,0:03:19.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Isn't this just an "heh?" type face!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.84,0:03:22.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So cunning, seems like it'll be really easy to accomplish!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.15,0:03:23.45,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Let's say it is
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.70,0:03:25.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This time, to complete the verification Hyouroku and Morita are gathered
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.68,0:03:27.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In the lounge of a fake show in which the former and the latter are starring together
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.76,0:03:30.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How many "heh?"s can be elicited?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.53,0:03:30.50,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,How many times
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.76,0:03:33.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He's quite out of touch, that guy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.43,0:03:35.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So even if it's a small thing
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.43,0:03:38.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I think he'll say "heh?", yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.57,0:03:42.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The time limit is 30 minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.16,0:03:42.39,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He'll probably say "heh?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.30,0:03:44.95,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Seems likely
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.94,0:03:46.60,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hyouroku wore a very bright jacket
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.60,0:03:49.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But TBS is really...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.55,0:03:52.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd never come back here again \N-How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.55,0:03:53.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No no, how to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.94,0:03:55.16,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Think he'll say it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.88,0:03:55.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, you are now, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.75,0:03:57.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You're not doing comedy anymore, pretty much?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.85,0:04:00.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Although I want to-to do it, but, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.69,0:04:01.65,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He's cute
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.96,0:04:04.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"LOVE it!" seems to be the one
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.74,0:04:08.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'll be on the Sunday episode
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.33,0:04:09.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh——
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.63,0:04:11.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh——
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.71,0:04:10.92,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.07,0:04:12.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is Kawashima on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.40,0:04:13.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Of course Kawashima will be there
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.77,0:04:16.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But it seems other comedians wont be
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.51,0:04:19.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Who will be?  \N-Probably an actress
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.14,0:04:20.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh——
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.48,0:04:22.11,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Too bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.38,0:04:21.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But it's really good
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.28,0:04:24.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I think it's Meru Nukumi, I think its been decided
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.68,0:04:26.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh——
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.06,0:04:27.84,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is an "eh?" person!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.57,0:04:29.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Although this junior does not say "heh"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.86,0:04:32.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He is definitely the type that says "eh-"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.88,0:04:33.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Next
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.97,0:04:36.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,She... she's a woman, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.39,0:04:37.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yeah, a woman
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.26,0:04:37.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.93,0:04:39.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Don't you know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.13,0:04:41.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I can't think of the person
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.02,0:04:43.75,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This person does not know anything
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.36,0:04:46.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He seems to be more out of touch than expected
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.39,0:04:45.74,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He doesn't even know her
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.74,0:04:47.46,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Does this guy not even watch TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.97,0:04:49.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Didn't Michopa go on TV?  \N-Oh, Michopa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.07,0:04:51.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You know Michopa?  \N-Michopa, yes, I do
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.34,0:04:53.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But the word Michopa...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.54,0:04:57.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It can't be broadcast in the northeastern region
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.95,0:04:58.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\alpha50}Eh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.75,0:05:00.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The word "Michopa"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.08,0:05:03.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Where is it in the northeast, Akita or Yamagata?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.15,0:05:02.29,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Very strong, Morita
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.29,0:05:03.54,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He's pretty good at this
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.49,0:05:10.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"Michopa" means "male genitalia"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.76,0:05:13.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Such a load of nonsense
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:15.33,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Very impressive
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.33,0:05:17.48,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Bullshit comes as natural to him as breathing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.57,0:05:15.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I don't know if it's the dialect or what  \N-Eh-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.53,0:05:19.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So Michopa can't even be seen on TV in the Northeast
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.64,0:05:21.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, is that right?  \N-Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.10,0:05:22.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.19,0:05:23.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But Michopa herself seems to have no idea about it
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.54,0:05:25.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then, if people in that region talk about Michopa...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.91,0:05:29.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If the interview is "Do you know Michopa?" then
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.08,0:05:30.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"Do you know XXXX", it'd be like that \N-Yeah, yeah, yeah
