Dialogue: 2,0:05:29.08,0:05:30.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\an4\p1\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord0\pos(476,1038)\clip(m 446 988 l 599 1060 592 1076 446 1012)}m 0 0 l 0 45 l 125 45 l 125 0
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.08,0:05:30.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\an4\p1\c&H1A29D4&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(476,1038)}m 0 0 l 0 44 l 122 44 l 122 0
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.75,0:05:32.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.22,0:05:34.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"Huh? What are you talking about?" This sort of thing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.15,0:05:35.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.95,0:05:37.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,+1
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.49,0:05:39.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's like that
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.42,0:05:38.60,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.59,0:05:41.72,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hyuoroku can't {\i1}not{\i0} say it
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.11,0:05:43.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Although the "eh" series was carried out
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.08,0:05:44.16,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's the score?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.30,0:05:47.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In ten minutes, not even a single "heh" has been elicited
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.92,0:05:49.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Next
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.26,0:05:51.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go to the bathroom for a little bit  \N-Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.55,0:05:55.59,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Here I was also considering the "eh" problem
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.59,0:05:57.25,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Indeed
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.37,0:05:57.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Here, Morita came out of the room and found the staff
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.74,0:06:00.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He's been saying "eh-" all along, right? That guy
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.80,0:05:59.97,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yeah
