Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.24,0:12:40.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That one is OK
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.47,0:12:43.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It doesn't say "Tamori" on the credits either
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.67,0:12:42.20,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,The type of person who says heh
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.20,0:12:43.86,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,A lot of talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.41,0:12:47.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00D6FF&\fs60}Heh~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.05,0:12:49.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Show businesses is amazing
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.01,0:12:48.37,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,A very long heh
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.37,0:12:49.22,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Super long
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.39,0:12:53.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Although he has successfully gotten a lot of "heh"s...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.22,0:12:56.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Did you watch the NASA press release? The news just came out in the evening
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.15,0:12:56.96,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,NASA
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.99,0:13:00.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It confirmed that although there is no heaven in the world, hell does exist
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.04,0:13:01.34,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Too much, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.80,0:13:02.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,NASA said that? \N -Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.67,0:13:07.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Did you know that the international rules of shogi are being changed to make it OK to repeat two moves?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.14,0:13:08.47,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Starting to fail
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.04,0:13:07.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Impossible
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.80,0:13:09.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, it means that a two-step move is going to be OK
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.31,0:13:14.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You can't. If you can repeat two steps, it's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.67,0:13:14.92,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's too fake, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.12,0:13:17.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,As the believability of the lies gradually decrease
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.41,0:13:19.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The number of "heh"s also began to plummet
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.83,0:13:21.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And so
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.52,0:13:26.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ota Pro seems to be retreating from show business
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.08,0:13:33.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They've proposed entering a new field, said "i'll do denim instead"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.93,0:13:32.61,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,A big lie
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.36,0:13:36.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Well, if Levi's could do it, it's possible I guess
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.03,0:13:37.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can Ota Pro make denim and sell it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.66,0:13:43.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Throwing accurate and reasonable remarks at crude and poorly thought out lies
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.05,0:13:41.85,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's true
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.85,0:13:43.70,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,The greatest truth of all
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.47,0:13:48.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Do you know the new flavors of Giggles coming out next year?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.47,0:13:48.44,note_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}※Giggle-kun (garigari-kun): Japanese lollipop brand
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.11,0:13:48.51,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,On the offensive again
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.05,0:13:51.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I don't know but i'm sure its quite unexpected
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.01,0:13:53.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It has the smell of petrol
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.28,0:13:55.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it won't sell
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.42,0:13:57.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They're now whispering words to each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.72,0:14:00.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So here it is time to reveal the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.09,0:14:06.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In regard to "heh"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.06,0:14:09.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In my understanding, Hirako is a person who loves to lie and blow smoke
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.77,0:14:12.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I just had the feeling of "Ah~ here we go again with this stuff"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.37,0:14:12.67,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,A suspect's expression
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.70,0:14:19.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, Alco&Peace's Hirako scores 5 points
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.69,0:14:16.41,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,But the results are pretty good
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.66,0:14:23.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The final challenger is
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.00,0:14:26.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Knights' Hanawa
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.35,0:14:28.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Who is your target?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.05,0:14:30.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's Master Oozora Yuhei
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.50,0:14:33.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A senior manzai talent
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.81,0:14:36.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Master Oozora Yuhei
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.97,0:14:32.29,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,The one everyone knows
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.29,0:14:33.54,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.92,0:14:38.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is bad
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.00,0:14:40.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Even holding a musical instrument in his promo picture
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.50,0:14:41.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,3rd tier, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.70,0:14:42.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.61,0:14:58.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Because he's 70 years old
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.55,0:15:01.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I think he probably doesn't understand youth culture
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.42,0:15:04.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I don't think i've even seen him using a phone
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.99,0:15:07.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Probably doesn't know how it works
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.79,0:15:11.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So it might be good to go down that kind of route
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.33,0:15:11.63,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.93,0:15:18.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time since you've been on TV like this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.26,0:15:19.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.44,0:15:23.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How many years has it been since TBS? About 7 years?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.34,0:15:21.78,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Very nice looking person
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.04,0:15:24.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Before was it for manzai work?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.44,0:15:25.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yeah manzai
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.80,0:15:29.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In terms of us, we come every day
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.44,0:15:30.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.78,0:15:33.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There is a late night TV shopping program
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.48,0:15:34.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Oh I know the one
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.22,0:15:35.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I do that one live
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.94,0:15:35.08,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm on that show
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.75,0:15:37.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, is it a live broadcast?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:39.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00D6FF&\fs60}Heh~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.32,0:15:44.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,About 6 days a week, working from 3:00 a.m. to 4:00 a.m
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.89,0:15:45.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00D6FF&\fs60}Heh~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.85,0:15:47.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sometimes until 5:00
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.03,0:15:50.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's very hard work, you don't get much sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:51.65,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,So gentle
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.50,0:15:56.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Basically, I don't sleep, I just go directly to the next job
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.78,0:16:01.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But wasn't TBS in decline for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.75,0:16:04.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There was a time they made a lot of money in Korea
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.88,0:16:07.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Isn't there a group called BTS?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.78,0:16:12.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That was originally a TBS group
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.46,0:16:12.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00D6FF&\fs60}Heh~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.82,0:16:17.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Originally a group selected by TBS through auditions
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.54,0:16:15.83,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, it's not
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.53,0:16:20.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then a guy named J.Y. Park came along {\c&H00D6FF&} \N-Hey~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.97,0:16:26.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And changed the TBS into BTS
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.34,0:16:28.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Now this group is quite hot in the United States
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.67,0:16:30.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They earn a load of money
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:31.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00D6FF&\fs60}Heh~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.74,0:16:34.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Royalties and such
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.02,0:16:35.40,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,A lot of high quality "heh"s
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.91,0:16:37.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Fascinated by everything
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.48,0:16:40.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Oozora Yuhei hits a "heh" streak
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.07,0:16:38.05,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,The level of a master
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.82,0:16:44.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And so we enter the previously mentioned topic of phones
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.69,0:16:49.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Signal...is your phone a smartphone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.03,0:16:54.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's a tablet, I have both a cellphone and a tablet
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.36,0:16:55.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You don't have a smartphone, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.46,0:16:56.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I have a smartphone
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.97,0:16:58.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You have both a smartphone and a tablet?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.17,0:16:59.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.24,0:17:01.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,An unexpected error has occurred
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:05.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The master is actually a wealthy man who owns both a tablet and a smartphone
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.28,0:17:07.74,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,So youthful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.92,0:17:08.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.48,0:17:10.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I don't seem to have any signal
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.08,0:17:15.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,My cell phone signal still has signal, it's normal
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.74,0:17:16.64,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He knows all about signal
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.35,0:17:19.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm connected at least, I can tell there's WiFi
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.39,0:17:21.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah here it is, it feels right to say it like that
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.54,0:17:23.34,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Cute
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.43,0:17:26.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Prior to the age
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.23,0:17:31.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You know, people below the age of 60 can see it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.06,0:17:35.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I can see the Wi-Fi signal hovering around
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.24,0:17:36.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The signal in this place is pretty pleasant-looking
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.83,0:17:38.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.11,0:17:38.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00D6FF&\fs60}Heh~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.78,0:17:42.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is this some kind of good guy competition?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.31,0:17:43.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This guy is too good for this
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.36,0:17:44.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Already looks like a good guy competition
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.84,0:17:46.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So does it go "poof" if you walk into it or something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.45,0:17:50.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you hit into it it just brushes past you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.66,0:17:51.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00D6FF&}Heh~  {\r}\N-You can't see it anymore, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.92,0:17:53.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can't see it at all, no
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.64,0:17:54.74,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Looks so happy
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.42,0:17:55.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Usually in the lounge people can always see it
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.66,0:17:57.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"The signal's strong today," so to speak
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.76,0:17:59.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00D6FF&\fs60}Heh~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.83,0:18:03.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,As the lack or possession of IT knowledge is tested
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.60,0:18:01.39,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He's a model contestant
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.86,0:18:07.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A big move leads to 3 consecutive "heh" explosions
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.11,0:18:09.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After this also
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.64,0:18:13.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I've been an M-1 judge for 4 years
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.58,0:18:17.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Did you know, the scores are already determined beforehand?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.28,0:18:19.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It must be like that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.84,0:18:21.89,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's not like that, master!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.89,0:18:23.68,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is really suspicious
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.72,0:18:22.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Before the show starts we're given the script
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.65,0:18:27.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Like "Matsumoto gives 0 points, Uenuma gives 0 points", that kind of thing
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.14,0:18:28.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Everyone looks at it beforehand
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.62,0:18:31.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's true
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.60,0:18:30.47,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.47,0:18:32.03,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why, master!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.03,0:18:33.25,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.25,0:18:34.47,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why do you think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.13,0:18:34.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Must've been decided long ago
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.11,0:18:38.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,5 minutes left on the clock
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.83,0:18:36.86,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Impressive
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.86,0:18:38.58,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,No matter what it is, it all works
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.41,0:18:42.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Next is the final sprint
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.41,0:18:49.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Recently there are more and more manzai newcomers joining Manzai Talent Association
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.21,0:18:49.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's a good thing
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.98,0:18:52.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Like Kaminari and such
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.78,0:18:55.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So apparently big things are about to change
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.32,0:18:59.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I've heard that this summer Downtown are gonna join Comic Talent Association
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.59,0:19:01.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't that be great?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.56,0:19:05.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The atmosphere in the association is quite good now
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.26,0:19:08.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If changes don't happen, the atmosphere in the association won't improve
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.03,0:19:12.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But in the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.64,0:19:17.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But haven't they said they want to disband? Dai-bon Sho-bon
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.51,0:19:19.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.74,0:19:21.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really? \N-So i've heard
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.61,0:19:27.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That XXXXX I went to a party with them
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.95,0:19:31.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Dai-bon's seniors and XXXXX's relationship seems to not be very good
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.54,0:19:34.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Relationship with XXXXX is not good either?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.15,0:19:35.25,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.25,0:19:36.84,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Don't say anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.84,0:19:38.20,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Went in a strange direction
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.02,0:19:41.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Didn't XXXXX have an argument with a mentor at the Manzai Newcomer Awards?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.60,0:19:41.79,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Stop it, stop it
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.76,0:19:43.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\alpha70}Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.96,0:19:48.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,As horror stories about Dai-bon that even he doesn't know begin to come to light
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.04,0:19:50.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Stop it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.01,0:19:52.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's this all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.77,0:19:54.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The truth is now revealed
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.18,0:20:00.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry, master, we've actually pranked you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.78,0:20:01.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Prank?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.76,0:20:02.58,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Cute
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.68,0:20:03.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.89,0:20:06.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wednesday Downtown
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.76,0:20:09.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh? But my hair is super messy
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.88,0:20:11.18,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's not the point
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.79,0:20:12.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I often have messy hair myself
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.73,0:20:15.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,By the way, the number of "heh"s...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.20,0:20:17.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You achieved a total of 21
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.05,0:20:18.18,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,So strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.23,0:20:19.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I must have an addiction...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.67,0:20:25.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H3732FF&}The result is\N{\r}Oozora Yuhei, please be extra careful about getting scammed
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.14,0:20:26.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Impressive
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.34,0:20:31.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Finally, the previous lies mentioned Matsumoto and Hamada
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.57,0:20:32.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Today, sure enough
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.45,0:20:35.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,With Matsumoto on a break currently, it makes all of this look pretty suspicious
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.06,0:20:38.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,With Matsumoto off today,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.73,0:20:40.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It looks like Hamada is a scapegoat for a lot of things
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.23,0:20:42.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What scapegoat? What am I a scapegoat for!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.58,0:20:45.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,All of this news is probably going to leak in about 2 weeks
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.54,0:20:50.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Let's welcome the next presenter
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.85,0:20:58.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Zun's Iio!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.78,0:21:01.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hello everyone in the bend, thank you for having me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.12,0:21:03.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Let's get right to it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.57,0:21:06.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The agency i'm a part of belongs to an office called Asai Planning
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.48,0:21:09.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,One of the great seniors there is Sekine Tsutomu
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.71,0:21:14.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What does everyone think of when they think of Sekine
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.22,0:21:17.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Imitation or something like that  \N-Indeed
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.29,0:21:19.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Imagination \N-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.61,0:21:22.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Someone who can create imaginative stories
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.36,0:21:27.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's right. 15 years ago, I witnessed Yuuka's parents steeped in an illusion
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.50,0:21:29.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Inside their minds?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.27,0:21:35.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, this time I bring you a theory about Sekine's specific skillset
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.67,0:21:37.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.89,0:21:45.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There is no successor to Tsutomu Sekine's art of impeccably introducing members of the public
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.76,0:21:48.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Nostalgic!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.25,0:21:53.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We all know the show "It's Okay to Laugh", right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.52,0:21:58.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is Sekine's swift description when a member of the public is features
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.17,0:22:02.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He would say something very appropriate to the characteristics of that person
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.74,0:22:06.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He'll say it instantly \N -Right
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.74,0:22:09.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"Three meals a day, all pasta" or something like that
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.31,0:22:10.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.73,0:22:13.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Very impressive  \N-Just one sentence
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.63,0:22:18.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The art of Sekine Tsutomu must not be lost
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.44,0:22:22.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So this project is to select his successor
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.33,0:22:23.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sounds interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.40,0:22:27.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The 2nd Generation Sekine Tsutomu Tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.99,0:22:31.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This time, comedians were asked to try
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.14,0:22:37.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The art of describing people who appear one after another with a short phrase
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.90,0:22:39.81,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sekine could really do it well
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.81,0:22:45.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,5 extras are randomly selected from a group of 20 people
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.31,0:22:47.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is that Hyouroku?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.44,0:22:49.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Definitely not
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.38,0:22:51.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,By the way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.06,0:22:53.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thanks for having me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.12,0:23:00.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sekine himself is the judge and will score the contestants' performance out of 10
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.62,0:22:58.94,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,A true successor
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.26,0:23:04.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The first challenger is
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.67,0:23:05.34,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is bad, these feet spell something bad
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.36,0:23:08.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.60,0:23:09.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.71,0:23:11.47,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He is really on this show a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.01,0:23:16.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Audrey's Kasuga, who was also a regular on "It's Okay to Laugh" as the same time as Sekine
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.71,0:23:19.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You're the first up
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.14,0:23:22.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Well it makes sense, since I have some experience
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.01,0:23:24.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I will be the successor to Sekine's style
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.64,0:23:25.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is that so
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.56,0:23:29.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So let's get started
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.14,0:23:30.43,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's hard to watch
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.15,0:23:32.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, please welcome the first person
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.12,0:23:37.13,note_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}BGM: Hiromi Goh - Oyome Samba
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.49,0:23:35.68,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,The song!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.68,0:23:37.13,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,The music is the same as the original
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.47,0:23:48.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Visits several fortune tellers in a row before getting the desired answer
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.33,0:23:47.72,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's good \N -Good
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.47,0:23:49.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,8 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.91,0:23:51.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A feeling of sincere yet slightly naive
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.91,0:23:55.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The kind of person who doesn't express their own opinion that much
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.85,0:23:58.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This hits the mark perfectly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.52,0:24:00.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Let's move on to the next person
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.39,0:24:14.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Caught a T-shirt thrown out by Hase Hiroshi at a wrestling match
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.07,0:24:16.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I can't believe he came up with {\i1}that{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.77,0:24:20.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is good
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.14,0:24:21.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,9 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.34,0:24:32.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Had a nightmare yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.13,0:24:32.18,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This can be said about anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.92,0:24:34.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,4 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.04,0:24:35.20,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah this one isn't good
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.82,0:24:40.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This "had a nightmare yesterday" is too blunt and thoughtless
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.32,0:24:42.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Being more specific about the nightmare would be better
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.94,0:24:44.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,For example
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.00,0:24:49.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Had a dream that all his teeth fell out yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.73,0:24:51.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you put it that way
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.47,0:24:54.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It would be a 7 or an 8
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.04,0:24:56.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Expanding on what nightmare it was would be best
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.26,0:25:12.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Able to beat someone up the first time they meet them
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.82,0:25:11.37,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Too much! \N-Too sloppy
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.52,0:25:14.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This one's too much
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.46,0:25:19.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The person being evaluated will probably feel bad after hearing it so it's not good
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.40,0:25:21.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's important to not hurt people's feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.13,0:25:22.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's for sure
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.23,0:25:24.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Because the other party is not in the industry
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.43,0:25:26.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If it's a comedian then it's fine
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.37,0:25:30.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But you shouldn't do it to a member of the general public
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.17,0:25:31.42,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,There are still rules
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.42,0:25:34.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Only by possessing the quality of consideration
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.01,0:25:40.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And not hurting the participants can one become the heir to Sekine's style
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.28,0:25:45.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But Kasuga isn't aware
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.64,0:25:54.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Husband embezzled a large sum of money
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.20,0:25:55.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is a prime example
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.90,0:25:57.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A public servant in Aomori
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.63,0:25:59.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.84,0:26:03.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But it's still kind of interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.34,0:26:08.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In summary, Kasuga's total score is 32 points
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.81,0:26:11.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.95,0:26:14.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Well done
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.52,0:26:18.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You had some good answers and some not so good answers
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.39,0:26:20.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I can't believe there's some that weren't good!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.49,0:26:22.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It only takes about a second, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.76,0:26:27.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You only have that amount of time to say something
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.56,0:26:29.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But your performance is more impressive than I expected
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.40,0:26:30.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.40,0:26:33.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can Sekine please say one?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.47,0:26:35.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If I were to say one...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.97,0:26:39.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The third one is a little on the heavy side
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.00,0:26:46.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Only the wife's whining and gout cannot be overcome
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.03,0:26:45.66,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not bad for him  \N-Good
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.18,0:26:47.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.55,0:26:49.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you just say "suffers from gout," it'll seem a little harsh
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.65,0:26:50.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It would be too direct
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.92,0:26:52.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}So add a little bit of the wife aspect first
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.99,0:26:56.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The demonstration of a pioneer
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.56,0:26:59.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The next challenger is
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.67,0:27:02.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thanks for having me
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.05,0:27:03.62,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This'll be good
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.62,0:27:07.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The Great King of Kansai, Laughing Rice's Nishida
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.11,0:27:10.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Nishida is very interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.71,0:27:14.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Good-looking face too
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.51,0:27:18.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Like a person in a Chinese ink painting
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.88,0:27:20.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Please can the first person enter
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.61,0:27:20.61,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Already going!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.50,0:27:24.45,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Always ready. It's a habit
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.01,0:27:26.55,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This one is difficult
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.59,0:27:31.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Still using mixi until now
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.59,0:27:31.76,note_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}※mixi：Social media platform established in Japan in 2004
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.30,0:27:33.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is a good one
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.10,0:27:38.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not trying too hard to be funny is a good approach
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.02,0:27:49.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Brought back a dog that was completely different from the one that ran away and kept it
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.32,0:27:54.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.58,0:27:58.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,She's indeed emitting the aura of regret regarding letting it run away
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.93,0:28:10.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Beaten by son with a violin
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.77,0:28:12.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is no good
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.54,0:28:15.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Such violence is not allowed
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.32,0:28:19.45,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Same person
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.33,0:28:28.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Offered Chicken McNuggets to the statue of The Buddha Jizo
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.62,0:28:28.76,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Differences in food culture
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.39,0:28:29.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.69,0:28:31.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,McNuggets are so effective
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.15,0:28:35.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The combination of "The Buddha Jizo statue" and "Chicken McNuggets" is great
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.47,0:28:45.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Massachusetts Institute of Technology
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.27,0:28:48.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.17,0:28:50.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Looks good with the glasses and looks like he has a good brain
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.17,0:28:54.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's also good that it ended at MIT
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.41,0:28:56.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.52,0:29:00.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Despite points lost for having violent elements
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.27,0:29:03.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He surpasses Kasuga with 36 points
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.39,0:29:04.53,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,If only he didn't say the violin
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.05,0:29:06.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The next challenger is
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.36,0:29:09.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.41,0:29:11.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Kano Eiko
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.50,0:29:15.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, let's have the first one on stage
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.35,0:29:17.47,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This MC is a firecracker
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.11,0:29:26.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,An assistant producer on Funny Manga Dojo
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.04,0:29:29.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.45,0:29:33.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I want to score a 10 on this one
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.48,0:29:38.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But nowadays, young people don't know "Funny Manga Dojo"
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.48,0:29:38.66,note_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}※A program broadcast from 1974 to 1994
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.76,0:29:40.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Therefore 2 points were deducted
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.66,0:29:43.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In my heart it's 10 points
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.45,0:29:52.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Installment fees are covered by us
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.47,0:29:53.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is a bit of a no-go
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.71,0:29:54.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,5 points
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.01,0:29:58.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A little underworld hint, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.84,0:30:02.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So what should you do with scary-looking people
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.01,0:30:03.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This one is...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.65,0:30:07.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Heaving a sigh, was supposed to quit 3 years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.59,0:30:12.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Who would say such a thing
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.46,0:30:14.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's kind of the opposite
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.39,0:30:17.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Fuji Takashi would certainly laugh at this
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.42,0:30:30.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Even carefully washes no-wash rice
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.37,0:30:31.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,8 points
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.78,0:30:36.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,She does have that atmosphere of carefully washing rice even if it doesn't need to be
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.28,0:30:50.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sells cicada shells for 10 yen
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.33,0:30:52.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,7 points
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.70,0:31:02.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Raised a cat that immediately ran away
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.06,0:31:04.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is 6 points
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.71,0:31:07.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm not really getting the same feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.02,0:31:14.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In summary, Kano overtook Kasuga with 34 points and reached second
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.61,0:31:17.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The next challenger is
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.99,0:31:20.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.96,0:31:23.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Razor Ramon RG
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.56,0:31:24.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, let's have the first one on stage
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.68,0:31:34.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Often resents blow drying her hair after showering
