Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.58,0:43:39.04,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It came from a program!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.37,0:43:45.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It aired on August 26th 2003
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.14,0:43:49.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Do you usually use this folding method?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.71,0:43:53.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I always roll up my T-shirt
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.11,0:43:57.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I have too many T-shirts so they can only be rolled up otherwise its impossible to store them all
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.95,0:44:00.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,My home is too small, they can only be rolled up for storage
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.40,0:44:05.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thus reveals Amamiya's status as a member of the Rolling School
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.58,0:44:11.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A professional father will not use this method
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.42,0:44:15.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Usually no one uses it
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.42,0:44:15.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.91,0:44:18.59,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.46,0:44:21.58,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Scary, a sudden appearance!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.70,0:44:25.02,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Drug Screening
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.44,0:44:28.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your hard work\N  -Hello
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.74,0:44:29.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.38,0:44:32.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I have a few spare clothes with me
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.52,0:44:33.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Bringing clean clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.79,0:44:36.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, I keep them on hand to change
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.23,0:44:39.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A technique appears!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.65,0:44:41.08,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,A standing fold
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.13,0:44:44.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A man who usually has no concern for storage casually uses this method
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.80,0:44:52.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The origin is the Ito family, whereas it's only user is the Kuro family
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.67,0:44:55.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Kuro family \N-An unexpected development
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.20,0:44:58.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's awesome \N -It is, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.04,0:45:01.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,When the staff investigated, it found that, aside from Kuro-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.10,0:45:04.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Kotouge and Zakoshi both use it
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.85,0:45:07.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Baldies love to use this trick
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.85,0:45:08.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.63,0:45:11.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It should be called "the bald people folding method"
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.42,0:45:13.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Only bald people fold clothes like this
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.49,0:45:18.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What was up with the violent cardboard method
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.47,0:45:19.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I can't believe they use cardboard boxes
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.27,0:45:21.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Didn't you see the cheers in the studio?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.53,0:45:23.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The Age of Peace \N -Bubble era?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.83,0:45:26.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A crazy era in which folded clothes can be an event
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.24,0:45:27.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Those people don't fold clothes like that at home
